#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.multiply.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.multiply"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:1 of
msgid "Multiply arguments element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素相乘参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:3
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:5 of
msgid "Input arrays to be multiplied."
msgstr "要相乘的输入数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播一致。如果未提供或为 `None`"
"，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于输出的"
"数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:17 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- The product of `x1` and `x2`, element-wise. Returns a scalar if "
"both  `x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- `x1` 和 `x2` 的逐元素乘积。如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是标量，则返回"
"标量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:23 of
msgid "Equivalent to `x1` * `x2` in terms of array broadcasting."
msgstr "等价于数组广播中的 `x1` * `x2`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.multiply.multiply:26 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

